            <thetext>Currently, the server response contains the data, messages and events keys, and the client checks whether the &quot;data&quot; key is present to determine if it is a qcl server response. This can lead to difficulties whenever there is a &quot;data&quot; key in the response from a non-qcl server. 

Solution: use an additional &quot;__is_qcl_response&quot; key to flag the response as a qcl server response.</thetext>
